location.fullValue: THE FLATS AT FULTON COURT CONDOMINIUMS
1549 S Florence Court Bldg F  Unit 603

data.description: Views, views, views! This amazing penthouse has stunning panoramic views of the mountains from every room! Come home and relax in the comfortable living room with engineered hardwood floors.  Share a meal in the dining room after cooking in the lovely kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, pantry, double stainless sink, and glass top stove plus JennAir stove top. Rest in the primary bedroom with a full bath and walk-in closet with extra shelves. Nice second bedroom too. Treasure the gorgeous views of the mountains and downtown Denver from the balcony or walk over to the clubhouse to enjoy the pool, fitness center, pickleball/tennis courts, and more!
